Sharvaya! Bhavaya!

29:17.291 --> 29:18.583
Thrinethraya!

29:19.458 --> 29:26.333
<i>Neelakantaaya! Bhasmangaraagaaya!</i>
Namasshivaya!

29:27.916 --> 29:33.208
<i>Jagadhbhurandharaa!</i>
Hormat pada Pranalingam.

